{"tid":2499025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本14歲少女被欺凌後自殺     生前被迫拍下裸照性虐待   求助老師卻未多次敷衍稱「我今天要陪男朋友明天再說」","createTime":"2021-04-21T14:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T14:53:29.000Z","uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"32956fdf1aeea0a3fff40498e6e44d3ab86deda7","tid":2499025,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQQedFrRHry5t6D7FYYcbbxkJ9g2wKKLeymiPrpuaBAEY?filename=Pd1xcPr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd1xcPr.jpg&h=d1656eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本發生一宗嚴重校園欺凌事件，一名14歲女中學生，長期受到學長學姐集體欺凌，被迫跳河、拍裸照甚至當眾自慰，照片其後在網上流傳，家長曾向老師反映卻被連番推搪，未獲積極跟進，最終她不堪受辱於今年2月離家出走，連日來杳無音訊，直至1個月後當地回暖積雪溶化，其遺體才在一個公園被發現。<br />\n<br />\n據日本媒體報道，來自北海道旭川市的廣瀬爽彩，自幼在單親家庭長大，於2019年4月入讀當地一間中學，自此過著煉獄般校園生活。參與校園欺凌的同學至少有1女2男，當時只有12歲的爽彩，被學長威脅影私密部位的裸照和自慰影片，否則會對她進一步性虐待，爽彩在恐懼下只好照做，其後裸照被一名學姐在通訊軟體「LINE」上發布，以致在網上流傳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaPyW6nkYdJpgfGKGsf9Cce6orKAFMMnKDQYMHXCRpQmk?filename=YSA2z3g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYSA2z3g.jpg&h=9f9a921c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<code>^被欺凌的14歲中學生廣瀬爽彩</code><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">母親4次向班主任求助未改善</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n爽彩自此萌生死念，曾向母親表示「媽媽，我想死」，其畫作也由過去充滿色彩變得陰沉。母親察覺女兒情況異常，曾最少4次到學校向班主任求助，但對方以各種理由推搪，更聲言：「那些孩子不會欺凌別人」、「今天我要和男友約會，明天再談可以嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n隨後欺凌行為愈演愈烈，爽彩被3名學姐帶到公園，現場還有數名同學，及在公園玩耍的小學生，她們要求爽彩當眾脫衣自慰，並帶她到小學殘廁繼續欺凌，她無法逃脫或求救，別無選擇下只好服從。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">被欺凌者迫跳河 遭誤會自殺未遂</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2019年6月，爽彩被至少10名欺凌者帶到約4米高的河堤，威脅她「若不跳下去，就要把照片給更多人看」，爽彩求情未果只好照做，有途人見狀立刻報警，爽彩的母親也趕到現場，那時欺凌者只在冷眼旁觀。當時一度引起關注，不過傳媒將爽彩形容為「自殺未遂」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVB2SxjGzLmGZRCFBS2A5HERQtXeajGJrhoyPtnJRQnsW?filename=uqm5xQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuqm5xQE.jpg&h=521a1a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRjt4TrqZbru9hdEooHBEjryuZ6YrmVXz4qPoexdgo3w9?filename=uBaeraF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBaeraF.jpg&h=22815c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n^廣瀬爽彩受欺凌後的畫作<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">零下17度離家出走</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至今年2月13日，爽彩在傍晚6時出門後便失蹤，當時氣溫只有攝氏零下17度，她曾在LINE上與友人作最後道別，表示「我想我今天會死」、「直到現在我都很害怕」、「我甚麼也做不了」，其中一人收到訊息後報警，令事件被揭發。警方接報後展開搜索，第二日更出動警犬和直升機，親戚及義工也組織搜索隊，但始終一無所獲，搜索行動在19日後中止。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">38日後溶雪揭伏屍公園</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n直至爽彩失蹤第38日，當地天氣稍為回暖，積雪逐漸溶化，爽彩的母親接到警方電話，指其遺體在一個公園被發現，身上只穿有輕薄衣物，相信死因為低溫症。"},{"pid":"b602be1f4b4fce27cda0b1840e427555bd588e7a","tid":2499025,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"其實日本人同支那人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ddfa6f54acf71ecc896ae79d4d8759ebdc8ff9","tid":2499025,"uid":76674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b602be1f4b4fce27cda0b1840e427555bd588e7a","tid":2499025,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"其實日本人同支那人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"唔食女優同尊重三文魚"},{"pid":"a641aa8be477f3d51bc47b16862cf8a145ba3035","tid":2499025,"uid":342990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b602be1f4b4fce27cda0b1840e427555bd588e7a","tid":2499025,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"其實日本人同支那人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"日本末落了"},{"pid":"607e619bebf4ca68ad1e862ee8e6862673374a82","tid":2499025,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"女人蝦女人。唔講以為女子監獄"},{"pid":"971d4bb8aed89f9cc7a82ba149d6ea4099c43318","tid":2499025,"uid":54552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:29:41.000Z","msg":"個女仔咁可愛都俾人搞 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9cf00f4865a896653b276e66f7a204950848f6","tid":2499025,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b602be1f4b4fce27cda0b1840e427555bd588e7a","tid":2499025,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:24:29.000Z","msg":"其實日本人同支那人有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"同香港人都無分別，滿意未？"},{"pid":"ce194a083a69c07584f6d8b585946610c1ab6abe","tid":2499025,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"畫作搞錯咗，第二幅係被欺凌之前的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢張係被欺凌前</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQt3PX9PtRECpnGfMDVdNv5G5G65DWoqN8CHQg3znByp7?filename=mpUVU6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpUVU6o.jpg&h=eb634b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢兩張係被欺凌之後</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSyW8jgrkTAbj91hY1Hm5TNW8J1tHMXAFx1x2nebtcVS6?filename=wxFYSTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxFYSTa.jpg&h=879a7e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeqGNzEh79LZrLx2QeAAtC1j1Lyg4qNEDeCMEYAUqPz9P?filename=H1kqxTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1kqxTb.jpg&h=c3335e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11fc093d5575a4ac334496f710f58b2348494d96","tid":2499025,"uid":319247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"個樣咁得意<br />\n如果生係香港<br />\n個女仔一早俾人當係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fec9ddaadbd94ca01006e450eba38517c9f2f3","tid":2499025,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce194a083a69c07584f6d8b585946610c1ab6abe","tid":2499025,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"畫作搞錯咗，第二幅係被欺凌之前的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢張係被欺凌前</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpUVU6o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpUVU6o.jpg&h=eb634b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">呢兩張係被欺凌之後</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxFYSTa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxFYSTa.jpg&h=879a7e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1kqxTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1kqxTb.jpg&h=c3335e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"爽彩在4月份開學不久後在一個公園讀書時遇到了1女2男中學生（A女B男C男）。<br />\n<br />\n因為看到爽彩好欺負，他們便開始對她下手。<br />\n<br />\n年紀稍微年長的兩個男生會逼着爽彩拍裸照還要求她拍自己自慰的視頻和照片給他們。<br />\n<br />\n其中一段爽彩和C男在社交媒體上的對話在出事後被複原出來了：<br />\n<br />\nC男：&ldquo;傳裸體的視頻給我，照片也行，不給的話，下次不帶套地做哦。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n當時只有12歲的爽彩很害怕，又不敢和母親說，于是便照着他們的要求去做了。但是讓爽彩沒想到的是，3人對她的霸淩變得更加過分了。<br />\n<br />\nA女還故意裝同情爽彩，還安慰道：&ldquo;你還好嗎？我站在你這邊的哦。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n然後馬上就轉過頭問C男拿了爽彩的裸照，還把這些照片發布到了社交媒體上，並在校園裏流傳開來，<br />\n<br />\n這讓爽彩蒙受巨大的恥辱，但她還是沒有勇氣反抗。<br />\n<br />\n有時候深夜淩晨B男還會叫爽彩出門，而有一次被母親阻止後爽彩卻說：&ldquo;被叫到了所以不能不去。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n十分擔心女兒的爽彩母親反複向班主任咨詢了4次，分別是4月1次，5月2次，6月1次，問女兒有沒有被霸淩，並讓她留意一下女兒的情況。<br />\n<br />\n但班主任似乎沒把這事放在心上，她甚至還似乎打消爽彩母親的擔憂：&ldquo;孩子們傻傻地鬧着玩，沒有霸淩這回事。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n因為沒有及時發現和幹預，爽彩受到的霸淩開始變本加厲。<br />\n<br />\n6月15日，爽彩被C男叫到了之前的那個公園。除了A女，B男之外，C男還帶來了D女和E女。<br />\n<br />\n當時在公園除了他們之外，還有很多在這裏玩耍的小學生，周圍也有很多人。<br />\n<br />\nB男和C男開始言語上侮辱爽彩，他們向新來的D女和E女表示，爽彩給所有男中學生發了裸照，還和他們撩騷。<br />\n<br />\n之後他們還逼迫爽彩當場進行自慰，稱&ldquo;就和你在視頻裏做的一樣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n意識到公園裏還有其他人，他們便把爽彩生拉硬拽地帶到了公園附近小學的殘障人士專用衛生間，在那裏强迫她自慰。<br />\n<br />\n因為被多人包圍着，無法逃離或尋求幫助，爽彩最終只能選擇服從。<br />\n<br />\n也正是這次事件之後，爽彩變得更加絕望了，她甚至放棄了抵抗。她沒有向任何人求助，而是繼續忍受着可怕的欺淩行為。<br />\n<br />\n但是魔鬼們並沒有收手，他們對爽彩的霸淩變得更加嚴重，最後他們還逼得爽彩跳河自盡。"},{"pid":"b4af5108bd17ac613081ef274ac60c5d49eb4765","tid":2499025,"uid":123591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"原來全世界既教畜都咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c1648c8835d4cfa083fc9887c3471dd861392f","tid":2499025,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea298f9428ed703730c07385a39e2a86e6b5aa6","tid":2499025,"uid":84734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:51:54.000Z","msg":"日本要轉校係咪好難？<br />\n點解咁都仲要繼續讀落去？"},{"pid":"041f87332d46f34a2be21268eb230daf9bf10933","tid":2499025,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11fc093d5575a4ac334496f710f58b2348494d96","tid":2499025,"uid":319247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"個樣咁得意<br />\n如果生係香港<br />\n個女仔一早俾人當係寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"成班兵，係虐待人地個位"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b2fec9ddaadbd94ca01006e450eba38517c9f2f3","tid":2499025,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"爽彩在4月份開學不久後在一個公園讀書時遇到了1女2男中學生（A女B男C男）。<br />\n<br />\n因為看到爽彩好欺負，他